data.description:
Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bath home with an array of inviting exterior features.   Step outside onto the back covered patio/deck, a perfect place to enjoy the outdoors in any weather. The long cemented driveway has ample parking space and continues into the privacy-fenced backyard with your very own private hot tub and fire pit.  Also, featured in the backyard is a concrete pad for your RV or fishing boat; plus, a "She-Shed" and insulated workshop w/electricity.

Walk into this open concept living space, with a kitchen nook, and separate dining area. This large kitchen features plenty of cabinets with lots of storage and countertops for preparing your wonderful holiday meals for family and friends.  The  primary bedroom has it's own bathroom suite boasting a dual sink vanity and a tiled stand-up shower.

This home is minutes from anywhere you would need to get to in Waco, from TSTC, Mclennan Community College, Baylor University, and Downtown Waco. Come check out this beauty for yourself and make it your home today!
